   version stable 1.60.0 1.50.0 1.12.0
   require gtk+
  optional crossfire-client-images '' ''            instead of downloading images during play
  optional crossfire-client-sounds '' ''            for sound effects
  optional SDL_image               '' --disable-sdl for SDL support
      opts --with-sound-dir=/usr/share/crossfire-client/sounds --disable-gtkv1
  category game
 attribute client x11
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL crossfire/crossfire-client/$VERSION/crossfire-client-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home  http://crossfire.real-time.com/
      desc 'the client for a multi-player graphical MUD
When creating a character press enter after typing in the name.
Clicking on Create Character will not work there.'
